      <title>杰里米·亨特在英国预算紧缩中陷入选民和市场之间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/jeremy-hunt-is-trapped-between-voters-and-markets-in-crunch-uk-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰里米·亨特下周的年度预算将面临艰难的平衡，他面临着实施引人注目的减税以在大选前提振处境不佳的保守党的压力，但同时也受到英国公共财政脆弱性的阻碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/jeremy-hunt-is-trapped-between-voters-and-markets-in-crunch-uk-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克努力阻止英国保守党向竞争对手巴德诺克倾斜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/sunak-struggles-to-halt-uk-tories-drifting-toward-rival-badenoch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威斯敏斯特的大多数人已经取消了里希·苏纳克赢得下届英国大选的机会。然而，亲密盟友担心这一挑战变得比应有的更加困难，因为他的一位内阁部长正准备接替他成为保守党领袖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/sunak-struggles-to-halt-uk-tories-drifting-toward-rival-badenoch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国家副主席敦促美国企业寻找新的合作领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/china-vice-president-urges-us-firms-to-find-new-areas-to-team-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京和华盛顿努力解决分歧之际，中国副主席敦促世界最大两个经济体的企业加强合作，维护全球供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/china-vice-president-urges-us-firms-to-find-new-areas-to-team-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 04:45:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 寻求与政治领导人达成协议以挽救改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/milei-seeks-pact-with-political-leaders-in-bid-to-save-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱总统提议与阿根廷有权势的省长和其他最高政治领导人达成一项协议，以保护其紧缩措施和自由化改革免受日益敌对的国会的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/milei-seeks-pact-with-political-leaders-in-bid-to-save-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 03:06:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将就 Meta 终止 Facebook 新闻的举措进行磋商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/australia-to-consult-on-meta-s-move-to-end-facebook-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Meta Platforms Inc. 表示将从 4 月份开始关闭 Facebook 新闻选项卡后，澳大利亚将与媒体组织进行磋商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/australia-to-consult-on-meta-s-move-to-end-facebook-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 02:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥领跑者与 AMLO 同步提议提高福利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/in-sync-with-amlo-mexico-frontrunner-proposes-boosting-welfare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥执政党莫雷纳党的总统候选人克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆(Claudia Sheinbaum)在竞选活动中提出了一系列提案，旨在建立巩固现任总统受欢迎程度的福利计划，并将自己定位为将继承现任总统遗产的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/in-sync-with-amlo-mexico-frontrunner-proposes-boosting-welfare</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 02:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地方检察官称，被控在时代广场袭击警察的男子身份被误认</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-02/man-charged-with-attacking-police-in-times-square-vilified-in-trump-ad-was-misidentified-da-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——一名委内瑞拉男子因涉嫌在时代广场踢倒一名警察，然后在出庭时关闭新闻摄像机而成为全国关注的焦点，周五检察官认定他在袭击中没有参与后，他被洗清了罪名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-02/man-charged-with-attacking-police-in-times-square-vilified-in-trump-ad-was-misidentified-da-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 00:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特要求养老基金披露英国投资水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/hunt-to-require-pension-funds-to-disclose-level-of-uk-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部将要求养老基金公开披露它们对英国企业的投资额，这是政府刺激它们增加对英国资产投资的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-02/hunt-to-require-pension-funds-to-disclose-level-of-uk-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地方检察官律师表示，法尼·威利斯丑闻并不构成罢免的理由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/fani-willis-scandal-doesn-t-warrant-her-ouster-da-lawyer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[检察官周五向负责不当行为听证会的法官辩称，富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯 (Fani Willis) 席卷乔治亚州起诉唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的丑闻并不能保证将她从干预选举案件中除名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/fani-willis-scandal-doesn-t-warrant-her-ouster-da-lawyer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 22:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将向加沙空投援助，希望斋月停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/biden-says-us-to-airdrop-gaza-aid-as-humanitarian-crisis-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登宣布，美国将与其他国家一起开始向加沙空投人道主义援助，以缓解以色列与哈马斯战争造成的日益严峻的局势，并表示希望斋月期间暂时停止战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/biden-says-us-to-airdrop-gaza-aid-as-humanitarian-crisis-worsens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 19:09:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
